data.description: ABSOLUTELY CHARMING Ranch Situated in Highly Desirable Subdivision on a Great Lot!! EXTREMELY CLEAN 3 Bedrooms & 1-1/2 Bathroom. Spacious Living Room w/Newer Carpeting & LED Lighting, Fully Updated Kitchen w/Quartz Counters, New Cabinets, Subway Tile Backsplash, Engineered Wood Floors, SS Appliances & Undermount SS Sink. Updated Bathrooms w/Ceramic Tile, Toilet & Vanities. Primary Bedroom w/Door Wall to New Cement Patio. Laundry Area w/New Cabinets & Quartz Counters. Attached 2+ Car Garage w/Opener, Vinyl Siding, Large Fenced Back Yard w/No Rear Neighbors & Perfect for Entertaining. Updated Electrical, 2-1/2 Car Detached Garage w/Opener. Close to Entertainment, Restaurants, Shopping, M-53, Library & Parks. Award Winning Utica Schools.
